tus/Getty Images)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Las Vegas Raiders v Buffalo Bills]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Samsung leaks its upcoming Fan Edition devices, including a phone, tablet and earbuds]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/samsung/"><ins>三星</ins></a>阿根廷网站的敏锐访客发现了一些意想不到的东西——新款 Galaxy Buds FE 耳机的产品页面，以及<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/a-samsung-galaxy-s23-fe-may-be-on-the-way-later-this-year-143559312.html"><ins>Galaxy S23 FE</ins></a>智能手机和 Galaxy Tab S9 FE 平板电脑的图片。正如<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.sammobile.com/news/samsung-just-leaked-its-entire-upcoming-fan-edition-lineup/" data-original-link="https://www.sammobile.com/news/samsung-just-leaked-its-entire-upcoming-fan-edition-lineup/"><em>SamMobile</em></a>所指出的，这是因为该公司泄露了其最新的 Fan Edition 设备。其中一张智能手机图像在设备上显示了 10 月 4 日的日期，这可能是对公告或发布日期的认可。</p><p>该公司尚未透露手机和平板电脑的任何规格。然而，据报道该页面上提到了 Galaxy S23 FE 和 Galaxy Tab S9 FE 的名称。这几乎是三星在没有新闻稿或拆包的情况下所能发布的最接近正式公告的了。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>产品页面（三星已撤下）确实<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.msn.com/en-us/lifestyle/other/leak-reveals-everything-you-need-to-know-about-galaxy-buds-fe/ar-AA1h6wsM#image=1" data-original-link="https://www.msn.com/en-us/lifestyle/other/leak-reveals-everything-you-need-to-know-about-galaxy-buds-fe/ar-AA1h6wsM#image=1"><ins>提到了有关三星首款粉丝版耳机 Galaxy Buds FE 的一些细节</ins></a>。它们预计将配备一个 12 毫米驱动器、每个耳塞中的三个麦克风（以增强主动降噪功能）和一个三路扬声器。</p><p>事实证明，三星的<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-s-21-fe-review-a-solid-remix-thats-unfashionably-late-143019388.html">粉丝版</a><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsung-galaxy-tab-s7-fe-release-date-140020033.html">设备</a>多年来一直很受欢迎。与该公司的旗舰机型相比，它们往往以更合理的价格提供可靠的功能。可以肯定的是，不少人会期待抢购今年的 FE 设备。</p><p>虽然这次泄露似乎是一个错误，但我们不能排除三星在正式宣布之前故意展示最新 FE 设备的可能性。每年的这个时候，各大硬件公司都在争夺您的注意力。就在苹果上周发布 iPhone 15 系列之前，谷歌发布了一些<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-reveals-the-pixel-8-design-ahead-of-apples-iphone-event-201331081.html"><ins>Pixel 8</ins></a>和<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/googles-more-durable-pixel-watch-2-will-be-available-for-preorder-october-4-180256306.html"><ins>Pixel Watch 2</ins></a>设备的预告片——谷歌的 Pixel 活动要到 10 月份才会举行。因此，三星可能一直在寻找有目的地泄密的头条新闻（在这种情况下，它显然起作用了）。</p><p>更有可能的情况是，这是该公司的又一次无意失误。它可能不像本周的<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/everything-we-learned-from-the-biggest-leak-in-xbox-history-161027198.html"><ins>Xbox 大规模泄密事件</ins></a>那样糟糕或具有破坏​​性，但无论如何，你可能认为三星现在已经知道得更清楚了。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/samsung-leaks-its-upcoming-fan-edition-devices-include-a-phone-tablet-and-earbuds-172156048.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/samsung-leaks-its-upcoming-fan-edition-devices-including-a-phone-tablet-and-earbuds-172156048.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> d8afcebf-bc30-4e74-b65f-e9df8d0c8c8a</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 22 Sep 2023 17:21:56 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1695403317</ingested><modified> 2023-09-22T17:22:13+00:00</modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Smart Phones]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="885" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/c2f38a10-596a-11ee-bbf6-cdd62e5a6292" width="1440"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="885" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/c2f38a10-596a-11ee-bbf6-cdd62e5a6292" width="1440"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Samsung]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Samsung Galaxy Buds FE earbuds, Galaxy S23 FE smartphone and Galaxy Tab S9 FE tablet.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Samsung Galaxy Buds FE earbuds, Galaxy S23 FE smartphone and Galaxy Tab S9 FE tablet.]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best smartwatches for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>就在几年前，购买智能手表的理由还不清楚。市场并不像今天这样饱和，功能也更加有限。如今，可穿戴设备世界充满了各种高质量的选择，Apple Watch、三星 Galaxy Watch 和 Fitbit Versa 等一些关键厂商凭借其智能功能脱颖而出。如果您正在阅读本指南，您可能已经决定是时候升级手腕上的任何小工具了 - 无论是标准手表还是老化的智能手表。无论您属于哪一类，在决定购买哪一款最适合的智能手表之前，您需要考虑的规格列表很长，我们将帮助您理解它。</p><h2>在智能手表中寻找什么</h2><figure><img src="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/59a8ed60-7819-11ea-a2fe-460c6da1595e" alt="智能手表上的 Google WearOS 界面。" data-uuid="472f010c-5b6c-3f53-b14e-d885b4a92446"><figcaption></figcaption></figure><h3>兼容性</h3><p>Apple Watch 只能与 iPhone 配合使用，而 Wear OS 设备则可以与 iOS 和 Android 手机配合使用。三星、Garmin、Fitbit 等制造的智能手表也与 Android 和 iOS 兼容，但您需要在智能手机上安装配套应用程序。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>智能手表操作系统还将规定您可以访问的第三方应用程序的类型和数量。然而，其中许多因素并没有什么用处，使得这一因素在宏伟的计划中成为相当次要的因素。</p><h3>价格</h3><p>最好的智能手表价格通常在 300 至 400 美元之间。与价格在 100 至 250 美元之间的廉价智能手表相比，这些价格较高的设备具有先进的操作系统、通信、音乐和健身功能。它们通常还包括机载 GPS 跟踪、音乐存储和 NFC 等额外功能，而预算设备通常不具备这些功能。</p><p>一些公司生产专门的健身手表：这些手表的价格很容易就超过 500 美元，我们只向认真的运动员推荐它们。泰格豪雅<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag-heuer-connected-calibre-e4-golf-edition-093031897.html">（TAG Heuer）</a>和宇舶表（Hublot）等品牌的豪华智能手表也可以达到天价，但我们不会认可其中任何一个。这些设备的价格可能超过 1,000 美元，而且您通常只需要购买一个品牌名称和一些不必要的异国情调的构建材料即可。</p><h3>电池寿命</h3><p>电池寿命仍然是我们对智能手表最大的抱怨之一，但最近还是有希望的。您可以使用 Apple Watch 和大多数 Wear OS 设备享受整整两天的时间。使用 Snapdragon Wear 3100 处理器的手表支持扩展电池模式，如果您愿意关闭除显示时间之外的大多数功能，则一次充电可保证长达五天的电池续航时间。 Snapdragon 的下一代 Wear 4100 和 4100+ 处理器已于 2020 年发布，但<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/razer-x-fossil-gen-6-smartwatch-gamers-160007878.html">迄今为止只有少数设备（其中一些设备尚未上市</a>）在使用它们。其他型号可以持续五到七天，但它们通常具有较少的功能和较低质量的显示屏。与此同时，一些健身手表一次充电即可使用数周。</p><h3>沟通</h3><p>任何值得考虑的智能手表都会向您的手腕发送电话、短信和应用程序通知。通话和短信提醒是不言自明的，但如果这些对您来说意义重大，请考虑使用支持 LTE 的手表。它们比仅支持 WiFi 的同类产品更昂贵，但蜂窝连接使智能手表可以接听电话，并且可以在设备不在附近的情况下处理短信。就应用程序警报而言，将它们发送到您的手腕上将使您可以向下看一眼表盘，看看您现在是否确实需要检查手机。</p><h3>健身追踪</h3><p>活动跟踪是人们转向智能手表的一个重要原因。通用手表应该充当健身追踪器，记录您的步数、卡路里和锻炼情况，并且当今的大多数可穿戴设备还具有心率监测器。</p><p>许多智能手表的健身功能包括内置 GPS，这对于跟踪跑步和骑自行车的距离非常有用。游泳者会想要防水的东西，值得庆幸的是，现在大多数通用设备至少可以承受在泳池中浸泡。 Garmin 等公司的一些智能手表比其他公司<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-07-16-the-best-gps-running-watches-for-2019.html">更注重健身</a>，并且往往提供更高级的功能，例如心率差异跟踪、恢复时间估计、板载地图等。</p><p>多年来，智能手表的健康追踪也取得了进步。 Apple 和 Fitbit 设备都可以估算血氧水平并测量心电图。但智能手表越便宜，它具有这些先进健康追踪功能的可能性就越小。如果收集这些健康指标对您很重要，您就必须为此特权付费。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-05/2c3e5710-b8b0-11eb-ae7c-3c5baecf0395" alt="三星 Galaxy Watch Active" data-uuid="12ad0f74-e120-3940-8958-bef3c90f1d40"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">恩杰特</div></figure><h3>音乐</h3><p>您的手表不仅可以追踪您的晨跑，还可以在您锻炼时播放音乐。许多智能手表都允许您在本地保存音乐，因此您可以通过蓝牙连接无线耳机并聆听音乐，而无需携带手机。那些没有内置音乐存储空间的手表通常具有手表上的音乐控件，因此您无需拿出手机即可控制播放。如果您的手表支持 LTE，则不需要本地保存 - 您将能够直接将音乐从手表传输到配对的耳机。</p><h3>常亮显示屏</h3><p>如今，大多数旗舰智能手表都有一些常亮显示屏——有些默认开启，而另一些则允许您通过调整设置来启用它。通过这项智能功能，您无需抬起手腕即可低头看一眼手表，即可查看时间、健康状况或您设置为在表盘上显示的任何其他信息。这无疑会影响设备的电池寿命，但值得庆幸的是，大多数常亮模式都会调暗显示屏的亮度，因此它不会不必要地以峰值运行。较便宜的设备不会有此功能；相反，他们的触摸屏会自动关闭以节省电池寿命，您必须有意检查手表才能再次打开显示屏。</p><h3>近场通信</h3><p>许多智能手表都具有 NFC 功能，让您无需携带钱包即可使用非接触式支付进行支付。保存信用卡或借记卡信息后，您可以在跑步回家的路上将智能手表靠近 NFC 读卡器来支付一杯咖啡的费用。请记住，不同的手表使用不同的支付系统：Apple 手表使用 Apple Pay，Wear OS 设备使用 Google Pay，三星设备使用 Samsung Pay 等等。</p><p> Apple Pay 是最受欢迎的 NFC 支付系统之一，支持 72 个不同国家/地区的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N1cHBvcnQuYXBwbGUuY29tL2VuLXVzL0hUMjA0OTE2IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3ZjQzNGUxNi1hYWJlLTMxNGQtODhmMC1mYWM3ZDNmMjZkNTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAT0rwaJ5r70d13bEq45AmZjeHIkXLUYaxQAHdothfWjt&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fen-us%2FHT204916">多家银行和信用卡</a>，而三星和 Google Pay 的支持区域较少。还需要注意的是，三星和谷歌系统对 NFC 支付的支持也因设备而异。</p><h2>整体最佳：Apple Watch </h2><p><core-commerce id="ed910031358149c299a1c4eb8ded84c3" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>通过<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ0hYOTNMWUwvcmVmPWZzX2Ffd3QyX3VzMT90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0yeS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiN2Y0MzRlMTYtYWFiZS0zMTRkLTg4ZjAtZmFjN2QzZjI2ZDUxIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAe03xh8N1he2NydxJHJIuH7WjUNe5fJ-r4BzwfaBFSdG&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0CHX93LYL%2Fref%3Dfs_a_wt2_us1" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CHX93LYL/ref=fs_a_wt2_us1">Apple Watch Series 9</a> ，该公司似乎专注于让你无需触摸屏幕即可与设备交互的方式。它引入了一种基于辅助触摸辅助工具的新双击手势，允许用户使用捏合动作来导航系统。例如，如果您无法使用另一只手滑动，您可以双击来调出您的智能堆栈或关闭警报。</p><p>该功能要到今年晚些时候才会推出，而且您无法在整个 watchOS 界面中执行此操作。但当它真正起作用时，它可以使小任务变得更加容易。在烹饪时关闭计时器或在跑步过程中启动锻炼追踪器只是双击可能非常有用的一些方式。</p><p>得益于全新的 S9 系统级封装 (SiP) 处理器，Apple 还为<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-series-9-review-freedom-from-touching-your-screen-130009764.html">Series 9</a>带来了设备上的 Siri 处理功能。这样，助手的响应速度会稍微快一些，但更重要的是，即使您处于离线状态，它也可以回答您。当您断开连接时，它可能无法提取网络结果，但它至少可以控制您的音乐和计时器。今年晚些时候，Siri 健康请求将会到来，你还可以向它询问你的睡眠、运动和锻炼数据。</p><p>凭借第二代超宽带 (UWB) 芯片、更亮的屏幕（夜间也会变暗）以及通过 watchOS 10 更新的界面，再加上新的“查找我的 iPhone”界面，Series 9 给人的感觉就像是一个肉肉的手机。从其前身升级。对 Siri 和无触摸交互方式的日益关注也是 Apple Watch 相对于竞争对手的另一个优势，该公司仍然是智能手表类别的王者。尽管在睡眠追踪方面仍落后于竞争对手，Series 9 仍然是目前最好的智能手表，尤其是对于 iPhone 用户而言。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-series-9-review-freedom-from-touching-your-screen-130009764.html"><strong>阅读我们对 Apple Watch Series 9 的完整评论</strong></a></p><h2>最佳预算智能手表：Fitbit Versa 2 </h2><p><core-commerce id="85b3305a467442a4bb55fa552af745fe" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>花 400 美元购买智能手表并不适合每个人，这就是为什么我们推荐<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9GaXRiaXQtRml0bmVzcy1TbWFydHdhdGNoLVRyYWNraW5nLUluY2x1ZGVkL2RwL0IwN1RXRlZEV1Q_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMnktMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjdmNDM0ZTE2LWFhYmUtMzE0ZC04OGYwLWZhYzdkM2YyNmQ1MSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAdjIwL4nz10RAZhyq20mYj-zj8OgDvtY0-Nv5KxaasDe&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FFitbit-Fitness-Smartwatch-Tracking-Included%2Fdp%2FB07TWFVDWT&amp;uuid=oDcdK5T2cT3u2dud18142">Fitbit Versa 2</a>作为 200 美元以下的最佳选择。尽管 Fitbit 推出了 Versa 3 和 4，但 Versa 2 仍然是我们最喜欢的经济型手表，因为它以优惠的价格提供了一系列功能。您可以获得所有这些必需品：Fitbit 可靠的运动跟踪功能（包括自动锻炼检测）、睡眠跟踪、防水、联网 GPS、血氧 (SpO2) 跟踪和六天的电池续航时间。它还支持使用 NFC 的 Fitbit Pay，并且内置 Amazon Alexa 作为语音助手。虽然 Versa 2 通常售价 150 美元，但我们看到它的价格低至 100 美元。</p><h2>最佳安卓智能手表：三星 Galaxy Watch 6 </h2><p><core-commerce id="0dd55d58db9349618f3ff2ebcacb93a0" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p><core-commerce id="256911007b3c40a68b5446b76dd6cfcb" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>对于Android用户来说最好的智能手表一直是三星Galaxy手表之一。尽管谷歌去年推出的 Pixel Watch 可能给该公司带来了一些竞争，但它在电池续航时间和内置功能方面仍然落后。今年凭借<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzc5MlFSVzYvP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTJ5LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3ZjQzNGUxNi1hYWJlLTMxNGQtODhmMC1mYWM3ZDNmMjZkNTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAQewAfITDJFLSlvax_O1tzwQKVXg4KnejQxO9pF8UxM_&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C792QRW6%2F" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C792QRW6/?th=1">Galaxy Watch 6 系列</a>，三星继续成为非苹果用户的智能手表之王。</p><p>该公司最大的优势之一是其标志性的旋转表圈，该表圈去年被取消，但在 2023 年的 Galaxy Watch 6 Classic 中又重新出现。该型号不仅复活了指尖陀螺式的戒指，而且比以前更小、更轻。边框稍薄，但仍提供流畅、有触感的方式来导航 Wear OS 4，而无需点击屏幕。与 Galaxy Watch 4 Classic 相比，这并不是一个巨大的变化，因此，如果您想仅根据尺寸进行升级，请不要期望有太大差异。不过，您会发现显示屏更亮，因此在阳光直射下更容易阅读。</p><p> Galaxy Watch 6 比之前的型号更引人注目的是其更新的健康和健身跟踪工具。机载皮肤温度传感器现在可以在夜间工作，以帮助跟踪排卵和月经周期，而新的睡眠指导工具可以更深入地了解如何获得更好的休息。 The company also added an irregular heart rhythm monitoring feature and will alert you if it detects anomalies in your cardio patterns. Runners will also appreciate the new personalized heart rate zones, which will help keep you precisely in the cardio ranges that are right for you, rather than those generated based on population data.</p><p> As usual, the Galaxy Watch 6 series also brings processor upgrades and some battery life improvements, alongside more apps optimized for your wrist. All told, the set of software updates coming to this year&#39;s model, including support for Samsung Wallet (instead of just Pay), make the Galaxy Watch 6 more useful than before. Just know that if you have a slightly older model, most of these will likely trickle down to your device soon. If you&#39;re considering trading in for a newer model, it&#39;s worth paying attention to the actual hardware differences. For Android users thinking of getting their first smartwatch, though, the Galaxy Watch 6 or Watch 6 Classic are the best all-rounded option available.</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/samsungs-galaxy-watch-6-review-evolution-not-revolution-120006375.html"><strong>Read our full review of the Samsung Galaxy Watch 6</strong></a></p><h2> Stylish smartwatches: Fossil and more </h2><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-01/7b17f630-523e-11eb-a357-6290b19b6ed5" alt="Michael Kors Access Gen 5e MKGO at CES 2021" data-uuid="5e1644f4-7ccc-3889-9910-693c96aaa9d7"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit"> Fossil</div></figure><p> Yes, there are still companies out there trying to make “fashionable” smartwatches. Back when wearables were novel and generally ugly, brands like <a data-i13n="cpos:11;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Fossil;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=b7221669-d5e1-47ff-8df7-36fe8547019c&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Fossil&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJiNzIyMTY2OS1kNWUxLTQ3ZmYtOGRmNy0zNmZlODU0NzAxOWMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZm9zc2lsLmNvbS9lbi11cy93YXRjaGVzL3NtYXJ0d2F0Y2hlcy8iLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjdmNDM0ZTE2LWFhYmUtMzE0ZC04OGYwLWZhYzdkM2YyNmQ1MSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAUP_s7ymco96jdPrWx1c2okIoCB3frKOa87__I4_1XMR&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fossil.com%2Fen-us%2Fwatches%2Fsmartwatches%2F">Fossil</a> , <a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Michael Kors;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=9b64e7e9-b6f0-4d91-bb71-eef8d80fabea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Michael+Kors&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI5YjY0ZTdlOS1iNmYwLTRkOTEtYmI3MS1lZWY4ZDgwZmFiZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubWljaGFlbGtvcnMuY29tL3dhdGNoZXMvc21hcnR3YXRjaGVzL18vTi0xbHExaThvIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3ZjQzNGUxNi1hYWJlLTMxNGQtODhmMC1mYWM3ZDNmMjZkNTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAW1mPU5BdK0D4GfHnK-OELERLJpl7xgeNhrWI8klrS77&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.michaelkors.com%2Fwatches%2Fsmartwatches%2F_%2FN-1lq1i8o">Michael Kors</a> and <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Skagen Denmark;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=de835634-eb1e-4390-bd94-e5983b38f543&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Skagen+Denmark&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJkZTgzNTYzNC1lYjFlLTQzOTAtYmQ5NC1lNTk4M2IzOGY1NDMiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2thZ2VuLmNvbS9lbi11cy9zbWFydHdhdGNoZXMvc21hcnR3YXRjaGVzLyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiN2Y0MzRlMTYtYWFiZS0zMTRkLTg4ZjAtZmFjN2QzZjI2ZDUxIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAclP_RzzZAQxGjhXKXymQLCukDvA9vfycrZ6Yr2Imrtu&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.skagen.com%2Fen-us%2Fsmartwatches%2Fsmartwatches%2F">Skagen</a> found their niche in stylish smartwatches that took cues from analog timepieces. You also have the option to pick up a “hybrid” smartwatch from companies like <a data-i13n="cpos:14;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAe3LQONW6fvKqYduhC8jHy9-Qw3EyKc2lHlBSrwvW2MA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FWithings-ScanWatch-Hybrid-Smartwatch-Oximeter%2Fdp%2FB08D6LNBPN%3F">Withings</a> and <a data-i13n="cpos:15;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Garmin;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=4c7f75f5-4803-438a-a506-12a0ccb4ede4&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Garmin&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI0YzdmNzVmNS00ODAzLTQzOGEtYTUwNi0xMmEwY2NiNGVkZTQiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ2FybWluLmNvbS9lbi1VUy9jL3Nwb3J0cy1maXRuZXNzL2Zhc2hpb24taHlicmlkLXNtYXJ0d2F0Y2hlcy8_IiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3ZjQzNGUxNi1hYWJlLTMxNGQtODhmMC1mYWM3ZDNmMjZkNTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAeNJTAOsCqs6v23yXaK7EXzpP8D5f_uxY0Tu1mWW0RXO&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.garmin.com%2Fen-US%2Fc%2Fsports-fitness%2Ffashion-hybrid-smartwatches%2F%3F">Garmin</a> – these devices look like classic wrist watches but incorporate some limited functionality like activity tracking and heart rate monitoring. They remain good options if you prefer that look, but thankfully, wearables made by Apple, Samsung, Fitbit and others have gotten much more attractive over the past few years.</p><p> Ultimately, the only thing you can&#39;t change after you buy a smartwatch is its case design. If you&#39;re not into the Apple Watch&#39;s squared-off corners, all of Samsung&#39;s smartwatches have round cases that look a little more like a traditional watch. Most wearables are offered in a choice of colors and you can pay extra for premium materials like stainless steel. Once you decide on a case, your band options are endless – there are dozens of first- and third-party watch straps available for most major smartwatches, and for both larger and smaller wrists, allowing you to change up your look whenever you please.</p><h2> Other smartwatches we&#39;ve tested</h2><h3> Apple Watch Ultra 2</h3><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:16;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQ0hYOU41OTQvcmVmPWZzX2Ffd3QyX3VzMD90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0yeS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiN2Y0MzRlMTYtYWFiZS0zMTRkLTg4ZjAtZmFjN2QzZjI2ZDUxIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAYVrUYwpLVmM1OnC6DJgV0UHXten0GB7L1f2LI_c2_SV&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0CHX9N594%2Fref%3Dfs_a_wt2_us0" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CHX9N594/ref=fs_a_wt2_us0">Apple Watch Ultra 2</a> is probably overkill for most people, but it has a ton of extra features like extra waterproofing to track diving, an even more accurate GPS and the biggest battery of any Apple Watch to date. Apple designed it for the most rugged among us, but for your average person, it likely has more features than they&#39;d ever need.</p><h3> Apple Watch SE</h3><p> The <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:17;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQkRIVFFEUlovcmVmPWZzX2Ffd3QyX3VzND90YWc9Z2RndDBjLXAtby0yeS0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiN2Y0MzRlMTYtYWFiZS0zMTRkLTg4ZjAtZmFjN2QzZjI2ZDUxIn0&amp;signature=AQAAAZrZg4pVPXDVws5oJSmSnVlWRt9yIiovZv_9mIYgDixh&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0BDHTQDRZ%2Fref%3Dfs_a_wt2_us4" class="rapid-with-clickid" data-original-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0BDHTQDRZ/ref=fs_a_wt2_us4">Apple Watch SE</a> is less feature-rich than the flagship model, but it will probably suffice for most people. We actually regard the <a data-i13n="cpos:18;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-watch-se-2022-review-battery-life-workout-health-tracking-144551799.html">Watch SE</a> as the best smartwatch option for first-time buyers, or people on stricter budgets. You&#39;ll get all the core Apple Watch features as well as things like fall and crash detection, noise monitoring and Emergency SOS, but you&#39;ll have to do without more advanced hardware perks like an always-on display, a blood oxygen sensor, an ECG monitor and a skin temperature sensor.</p><h3> Google Pixel Watch</h3><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:19;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-pixel-watch-review-battery-life-fitbit-heart-rate-sensing-015412121.html">Google Pixel Watch</a> debuted in 2022 after many years of rumors, and it served as the first marriage of Google&#39;s WearOS and Fitbit&#39;s expertise in the health-monitoring space (Google purchased Fitbit back in 2021). While it&#39;s a capable smartwatch, its short battery life and strange Fitbit inclusions hold it back from being a true competitor for the Apple Watch and Samsung&#39;s Galaxy Watches.</p><h3> Garmin Forerunner 745</h3><p> The Garmin Forerunner 745 is an excellent <a data-i13n="cpos:20;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-gps-running-watch-141513957.html">GPS running watch</a> for serious athletes or those who prize battery life above all else. When we tested it, we found it to provide accurate distance tracking, a killer 16-hour battery life with GPS turned on (up to seven days without it) and support for onboard music storage and Garmin Pay.</p> This article originally appeared on Engadget at https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/best-smartwatches-153013118.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 7f434e16-aabe-314d-88f0-fac7d3f26d51</guid><dc:creator> Valentina Palladino,Cherlynn Low</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 22 Sep 2023 17:15:07 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1695404668</ingested><modified> 2023-09-22T17:44:47+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[news]]></category><category><![CDATA[smartwatch]]>